You have accused me of lieing multiple times, but in the course of your posts, it is easy to detect contradictions and inconsistencies on your part aas well- I'll make you a deal, a stack of ore for every outright falsehood of yours I can back up with another of your own posts.  <br>
<br>
&quot;When I have been discourteous before this incident to you or any Vision member&quot;<br>
<br>
